Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.82,0:23:06.82,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,Hey. I'm Rakuro Hizutome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.62,0:23:09.28,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.12,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,I'm a trash game hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.54,0:23:14.96,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,Why do I love trash games so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:19.17,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,There's a saying. \N"Seek out trials while you're young."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.67,0:23:31.26,Sign_Basic,sign,0,0,0,,{\pos(954,218.001)\an7\fs48\fnTimes New Roman\c&H000000&\b1\bord3\shad0\3c&HFFFFFF&}"Seek out trials while you're young." \N If you struggle while you're young,\Nthe experience will be useful later,\Nso you should aggressively pursue trials.\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hFrom Kojien, 7th Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.17,0:23:21.42,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,My name, "Rakuro," already means easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:25.68,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,so why should I seek out \Nthe easy path in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:28.14,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,Actively seeking out the most difficult paths
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.14,0:23:31.26,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,and climbing the most \Ntreacherous mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.27,0:23:37.52,Default,Rakuro,0,0,0,,That's where you'll see the most beautiful \Nviews, and the most enjoyable life!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.03,0:23:51.66,Sign_Basic,sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(60,750)\an7\fnTimes New Roman\b1\fs84\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0}This daydream is fiction. It has no relation to actual\Npeople or trash game hunters.
